        </div>
        <div class="portfolio-item">
          <img src="/fashion_.jpg" alt="Fashion Photography" />
        </div>
        <div class="portfolio-item">
          <img src="/0402_ai_people_018.jpg" alt="AI Generated People" />
        </div>
        <div class="portfolio-item">
          <img src="/header_bull.jpg" alt="Bull Header Image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            I am a creative hands-on entrepreneur with nearly 20 years of experience in film making and post production.
