          <p>
            My work combines technical expertise with artistic vision, creating visuals that challenge perception and 
            explore the intersection of reality and imagination. I collaborate with brands and artists to develop 
            forward-thinking narratives and visual experiences.
          </p>
          <div class="tools">
            <span class="tool">Kling</span>
